26146, 	"Create <b>Ballista Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 25s; Heavy cavalry equipped with a Scorpion. <hp>; <attack> (+8 vs. Ships, +5 vs. Buildings, +3 extra vs. Stone Defense); Reload time: 2.5; Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/3 (-2 Armor (2 extra dmg) each against anti-Cavalry, anti-Elephant and anti-Siege dmg); Range: 5 <i>(SE 6)<i>; Accuracy: 100%; Classes: Cavalry, Siege, Elephants, Unique Units; Speed: 0.8; Attack delay: 0.28s; Line of sight: 7; <i>Can cut trees<i>" 
26147, 	"Create <b>Elite Ballista Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 25s; Heavy cavalry equipped with a Scorpion. <hp>; <attack> (+8 vs. Ships, +3 vs. Spearmen, +8 vs. Buildings, +4 extra vs. Stone Defense); Reload time: 2.5; Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/3 (-2 Armor (2 extra dmg) each against anti-Cavalry, anti-Elephant and anti-Siege dmg); Range: 5 <i>(SE 6)<i>; Accuracy: 100%; Classes: Cavalry, Siege, Elephants, Unique Units; Speed: 0.8; Attack delay: 0.28s; Line of sight: 7; <i>Can cut trees<i>" 
26148, 	"Create <b>Karambit Warrior<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 6s (<i>Conscription<i>: 4.5s); Cheap and weak infantry unit that only takes half a population slot.\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Eagles, (<i>Arson: +2 vs. Buildings<i>)); Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/1; Range: 0\nClasses: Infantry, Unique Units; Speed: 1.2; Line of sight: 3" 
26150, 	"Create <b>Elite Karambit Warrior<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 6s (<i>Conscription<i>: 4.5s); Cheap and weak infantry unit that only takes half a population slot.\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Eagles, +1 (+3) vs. Buildings); Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 1/1; Range: 0\nClasses: Infantry, Unique Units; Speed: 1.2; Line of sight: 3" 
26151, 	"Create <b>Arambai<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 21s (<i>Conscription<i>: 15.8s); Powerful, but inaccurate mounted dart thrower. <i>Not affected by range/attack upgrades or Parthian Tactics<i>\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Rams); Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/2; Range: 5; Accuracy: 20%; Classes: Cavalry, Archers, Cavalry Archers, Unique Units; Speed: 1.30; Attack delay: 0.7s; Line of sight: 7" 
26152, 	"Create <b>Elite Arambai<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 21s (<i>Conscription<i>: 15.8s); Powerful, but inaccurate mounted dart thrower. <i>Not affected by range/attack upgrades or Parthian Tactics<i>\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Rams); Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 1/3; Range: 5; Accuracy: 30%; Classes: Cavalry, Archers, Cavalry Archers, Unique Units; Speed: 1.30; Attack delay: 0.7s; Line of sight: 7" 
26165, 	"Create <b>Rattan Archer<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 16s (<i>Conscription<i>: 12s); Archer with high pierce armor.\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Spearmen, <i>Saracen ally: +2 vs. Buildings<i>); Reload time: 2 (<i>TR<i> 1.7); Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/4; Range: 4; Accuracy: 80%\nClasses: Archers, Unique Units; Speed: 1.1; Attack delay: 0.35s; Line of sight: 6 (<i>Magyar ally<i> 8)" 
26166, 	"Create <b>Elite Rattan Archer<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 16s (<i>Conscription<i>: 12s); Archer with high pierce armor.\n<hp>; <attack> (+2 vs. Spearmen, <i>Saracen ally: +2 vs. Buildings<i>); Reload time: 2 (<i>TR<i> 1.7); Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/6; Range: 5; Accuracy: 90%\nClasses: Archers, Unique Units; Speed: 1.1; Attack delay: 0.35s; Line of sight: 6 (<i>Magyar ally<i> 8)" 
26167, 	"Create <b>Battle Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 24s; Slow and heavy cavalry, weak to Halbs and Monks.\n<hp>; <attack> (+4 vs. Buildings, +4 extra vs. Stone Defense), Blast damage: Attack/2, Blast Radius: 0.4; Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 1/2; Range: 0\nClasses: Cavalry, Elephants; Speed: 0.85 (0.94); Line of sight: 4" 
26168, 	"Create <b>Elite Battle Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 24s; Slow and heavy cavalry, weak to Halbs and Monks.\n<hp>; <attack> (+7 vs. Buildings, +7 extra vs. Stone Defense), Blast damage: Attack/2, Blast Radius: 0.4; Reload time: 2; Melee/Pierce Armor: 1/3; Range: 0\nClasses: Cavalry, Elephants; Speed: 0.85 (0.94); Line of sight: 5" 
26190, 	"Create <b>Imperial Skirmisher<b> (<cost>)\nCreation time 22s (<i>Briton ally 18.3s<i>); Vietnamese mercenary unit, available when teamed with a Vietnamese player. Good against Archers, Spearmen; weak vs. other units.\n<hp>; <attack> (+5 vs. Archers, +3 extra vs. Cavalry Archers, +3 vs. Spear-line); Reload time: 3; Melee/Pierce Armor: 0/5; Range: 5 (min: 1); Accuracy: 95% (<i>TR 100%<i>); Class: Archers; Attack delay: 0.35s; Speed: 0.96; Line of sight: 7" 
26249, 	"Build <b>Harbor<b> (<cost>)\nUsed to build and improve ships, deposit food from Fishing Ships, and trade with other players by sea. Automatically attacks enemy units and buildings within range.\n<hp>; <attack> (+10 vs. Ships) + 3x 1 dmg arrows; Reload time: 3; Melee/Pierce Armor: 3/10; Range: 7; Accuracy: 100%\nClass: Buildings, Stone Defense; Line of sight: 10" 
28247, 	"Upgrade to <b>Elite Ballista Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 1:10 (<i>Conscription<i> 53s)\nUpgrades your Ballista Elephants and lets you create Elite Ballista Elephants, which are stronger (+1 Attack, +3 vs. Spearmen, +3 vs. Buildings, +1 vs. Stone Defense, +50 HP)." 
28248, 	"Upgrade to <b>Elite Karambit Warrior<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nUpgrades your Karambit Warriors and lets you create Elite Karambit Warriors, which are stronger (+1 Attack, +1 vs. Buildings) and better armored (+1 Melee Armor, 10 HP)." 
28289, 	"Upgrade to <b>Elite Arambai<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 1:05 (<i>Conscription<i> 51s)\nUpgrades your Arambais and lets you create Elite Arambais, which are stronger (+2 Attack, +10% accuracy) and better armored (+1 Pierce Armor, +2 against anti-Cavalry Archer dmg, +5 HP)." 
28290, 	"Upgrade to <b>Elite Rattan Archer<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 45s (<i>Conscription<i> 34s)\nUpgrades your Rattan Archers and lets you create Elite Rattan Archers, which are stronger (+1 Attack, +1 range, +10% accuracy) and better armored (+2 Pierce Armor, +10 HP." 
28299, 	"Upgrade to <b>Elite Battle Elephant<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 1:40 (<i>Conscription<i> 1:15)\nUpgrades your Battle Elephants and lets you create Elite Battle Elephants, which are stronger (+4 Attack, +3 vs. Buildings,Stone Defense) and better armored (+1 Pierce Armor, +50 HP)." 
28300, 	"Upgrade to <b>Imperial Skirmisher<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 45s (<i>Conscription<i> 34s)\nUpgrades your Elite Skirmishers and lets you create Imperial Skirmishers, which are stronger (+1 Attack, +1 vs. Archers, +1 extra vs. Cavalry Archers, +5% accuracy) and better armored (+1 Pierce Armor)." 
28291, 	"Research <b>Tusk Swords<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nBattle Elephants get +3 Attack" 
28292, 	"Research <b>Double Crossbow<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nBallista Elephants and Scorpions shoot two projectiles.\n<b>Scorpions<b>: Second bolt has 50% of the strength of the first bolt.\n<b>Ballista Elephants<b>: Second bolt 6 Pierce Attack, +3 vs. Elephants, +1 vs. Buildings" 
28293, 	"Research <b>Thalassocracy<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nUpgrades your Docks to Harbors, which fire arrows (1 main arrow: 6 Pierce, +13 vs. Ships, affected by Blacksmith upgrades, Chemistry; 3 extra arrows: 1 damage each)." 
28294, 	"Research <b>Forced Levy<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nMilitia-line gold cost is replaced by additional food cost." 
28295, 	"Research <b>Howdah<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nBattle Elephants get +1/+1 Armor." 
28296, 	"Research <b>Manipur Cavalry<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nCavalry and Arambai deal +6 bonus attack vs. Buildings. Half of that can be blocked by building armor (e.g. of a castle or masonry research)" 
28297, 	"Research <b>Chatras<b> (<cost>)\nResearch time 40s (<i>Conscription<i> 30s)\nBattle Elephants get +50 HP." 
